from the bad memories.

303
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:56,326
What bad memories?

304
00:13:56,350 --> 00:14:00,076
He was the Philly mayor in 1985,

305
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:03,376
when the MOVE bombing happened.

306
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:06,296
What happened again?

307
