MOVE is a communal Black liberation

308
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:10,646
and environmentalist organization

309
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:13,566
founded in the 1970s by a man

310
00:14:13,590 --> 00:14:15,786
who renamed himself John Africa.

311
00:14:15,810 --> 00:14:17,436
Yeah, my dad wasn't
a member of MOVE,

312
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,826
but he liked parts of their cause.

313
00:14:18,850 --> 00:14:20,916
They're a religious,
pro-nature community.

314
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:23,356
Well, apparently
they rejected modern life

315
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:25,486
and dependence on technology.

316
