532
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,736
Well, triple check that inventory.

533
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:57,996
And if you come short on
anything, even a tiny amount,

534
00:22:58,020 --> 00:22:59,850
call us right away, OK?

535
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:06,576
I don't know what I can tell you.

