00:23:15,430 --> 00:23:18,016
Did Gerry and his family
belong to MOVE?

542
00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:20,830
Kids, wait for me.

543
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:25,416
No, Gerry has nothing to do with that.

544
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,416
But his family lived on that block.

545
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:29,636
And what happened in 1985,
it destroyed them.

546
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:31,596
Their house burned down, right?

547
00:23:31,620 --> 00:23:33,036
Yes, but it wasn't about losing the house.

548
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:34,776
It was about losing his home.

549
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:37,776
Gerry's parents never recovered.

550
