I filed for divorce last year,

557
00:23:56,950 --> 00:23:59,106
but I stayed close by for the kids.

558
00:23:59,130 --> 00:24:00,276
Do you guys share custody?

559
00:24:00,300 --> 00:24:01,626
For now.

560
00:24:01,650 --> 00:24:03,626
But since he lost his job
and then the house

561
00:24:03,650 --> 00:24:05,236
if the kids have nowhere
to stay with him,

562
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:06,716
I might as well move to Phoenix.

563
00:24:06,740 --> 00:24:08,376
My sister lives out there.

564
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:10,816
It's so much cheaper.

565
00:24:10,840 --> 00:24:13,856
Does Gerry know you want
custody of the kids?

566
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:15,466
I'm not trying to blindside him.

567
00:24:15,490 --> 00:24:17,646
I told him a few weeks ago.

568
00:24:17,670 --> 00:24:19,816
And how did he react?

569
00:24:19,840 --> 00:24:22,606
Worse than when I told him
I wanted a divorce.

570
00:24:22,630 --> 00:24:25,656
Back then, I had to hide
all the meds in our house.

571
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:27,006
I was scared he might do something

572
00:24:27,030 --> 00:24:28,306
he couldn't take back.

573
00:24:28,330 --> 00:24:29,640
He already has.

574
00:24:32,420 --> 00:24:34,420
Two people are dead.

575
00:24:36,910 --> 00:24:38,430
What?

576
00:24:41,780 --> 00:24:44,066
Our kids are Gerry's world.

577
00:24:44,090 --> 00:24:45,586
And they adore him back.

578
00:24:45,610 --> 00:24:48,456
When they find out what
he's done, it'll destroy them.

579
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:50,376
When's the last time
you spoke with him?

580
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:52,196
A couple weeks ago.

581
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:54,416
Gerry called me from a number
I didn't recognize.

582
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,530
Let's give it a try.

583
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:01,946
<i>Brooklyn Men's Emergency Shelter.</i>

