00:29:20,620 --> 00:29:21,906
Gerry told a friend that
when his house burned down,

712
00:29:21,930 --> 00:29:23,036
the fire department just
stood by and did nothing.

713
00:29:23,060 --> 00:29:24,086
Is that true?

