00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,606
His last known is in Brooklyn.

756
00:30:58,630 --> 00:30:59,956
You and Ray go see
the fire commissioner.

757
00:30:59,980 --> 00:31:01,420
The rest of you, with me.

758
00:31:09,300 --> 00:31:11,496
Damn incident derailed my career.

759
00:31:11,520 --> 00:31:13,106
By incident, you mean
the bomb you ordered

760
00:31:13,130 --> 00:31:14,326
that killed 11 people?

761
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:16,196
It wasn't just any person.

762
00:31:16,220 --> 00:31:19,326
They were disrupting the city
and endangering the police.

763
00:31:19,350 --> 00:31:20,546
What about the five kids?

764
00:31:20,570 --> 00:31:22,986
How were they endangering the police?

765
00:31:23,010 --> 00:31:25,896
I mean, those five kids weren't
the only collateral damage.

766
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:28,986
200 homes burnt that day.

767
00:31:29,010 --> 00:31:29,987
This is Gerry Colworth.

768
00:31:30,011 --> 00:31:31,256
He lost his childhood home.

769
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:32,736
Do you recognize him?

770
00:31:32,760 --> 00:31:34,346
No.

771
00:31:34,370 --> 00:31:36,566
But I do remember the Colworth name.

772
00:31:36,590 --> 00:31:38,346
His parents were part
of a lawsuit against the city

773
00:31:38,370 --> 00:31:40,046
and your police department.

774
00:31:40,070 --> 00:31:42,656
That's right.

775
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:47,526
First time I saw her in court,
Loretta Colworth was pregnant.

